Text:
Hey Rosa

     I hate to be a bother Rosa, but could you please reseed or what have have you.  Perhaps most if not all of your CC Vids, I really do appreciate them to all outside but even your Karma Chameleon has been stalled at 97.07% for a while now.  Your CC vids are the best I have seen yet and I really enjoyed them live at TOTP, it was brilliant, thanks for taking the time to bring them to us.  

But if you Could reseed  most of them, the ones that need reseeding, which is most of them, if not all by now, thanks.
